{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"b710473f-e409-4df9-a888-f9dc0351d5f5","content":"No files found in the working directory. I'll provide the solution directly.\n\n## Converting to Compiled Bindings\n\nAdd `x:DataType` to your `ContentPage` to enable compiled bindings:\n\n```xml\n<ContentPage xmlns=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/dotnet/2021/maui\"\n             xmlns:x=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2009/xaml\"\n             xmlns:vm=\"clr-namespace:YourApp.ViewModels\"\n             x:Class=\"YourApp.Views.SettingsPage\"\n             x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\">\n\n    <VerticalStackLayout Padding=\"20\" Spacing=\"15\">\n\n        <Entry Text=\"{Binding Theme}\" Placeholder=\"Theme\" />\n\n        <Switch IsToggled=\"{Binding NotificationsEnabled}\" />\n\n        <Stepper Value=\"{Binding FontSize}\" Minimum=\"8\" Maximum=\"48\" />\n        <Label Text=\"{Binding FontSize, StringFormat='Font Size: {0}'}\" />\n\n    </VerticalStackLayout>\n</ContentPage>\n```\n\n**Key changes:**\n1. Added `xmlns:vm` for your ViewModel namespace.\n2. Added `x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\"` on the root element — this tells the XAML compiler the type of BindingContext.\n\n## Catching Binding Errors at Build Time\n\nWith `x:DataType` in place, the compiler validates bindings against the declared type. To **ensure errors break the build**, add this to your `.csproj`:\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n    <!-- Treat XAML binding warnings as errors -->\n    <WarningsAsErrors>$(WarningsAsErrors);XC0045</WarningsAsErrors>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\n`XC0045` is the diagnostic for compiled binding failures (e.g., misspelled property names or type mismatches). Now a typo like `{Binding Themee}` will produce a **build error** instead of silently failing at runtime.\n\n**Tips:**\n- If you need to opt out for a specific element (e.g., a `DataTemplate` with a different type), use `x:DataType` locally on that element.\n- Use `x:DataType=\"\"` to disable compiled bindings for a subtree where the type isn't known statically.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"5d3f5f9d-4159-4a31-b938-55166aaf8147","outputTokens":551,"requestId":"4844:386B3C:539C54C:5BB95F4:69F3FA07"},"id":"7638e091-3cff-45c2-9b5a-c6f0fb061b01","timestamp":"2026-05-01T00:55:47.327Z","parentId":"2b97fe9f-9fd6-4e1e-8477-42b512cb9032"}
